          "date": "2019-01-10 20:28:52.000000000",
          "tz": -300
        },
        "subject": "LU-11691 llapi: PFL layout size limit",
        "message": "LU-11691 llapi: PFL layout size limit\n\nThe PFL code does not correctly check for overflowing the\nlayout size limits by putting many stripes in multiple\ncomponents.\n\nAdd a check that limits the total stripes in a PFL file to\n1.5 times MAX_STRIPE_COUNT.  The extra 50% allows the last\ncomp of a PFL file to have MAX_STRIPE_COUNT, and makes it\npossible to mirror a file using MAX_STRIPE_COUNT to a\nsmaller (but still large) number of OSTs.\n\nSigned-off-by: Patrick Farrell <pfarrell@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: I97da7e4c4aaf96896146251879112f278036f2e8\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
